<P>Cubite is an extremely hard to find mineral. It's lightweight, strong =
and=20
malleable.</P>
<P>When added to other metals, even a tiny amount of Cubite can increase =

durability by 50%. Any colony with access to Cubite will receive a 15%=20
cumulative development bonus. While rare, Cubite is not as rare as the =
other=20
super luxuries.</P>
<P>Cubite will only be found on asteroids.</P>
<P>Occurance: very rare.</P>
<P>Type: Luxury resource.</P></FONT></DIV></BODY></HTML>

